(188, 4, '2014-06-12 09:10:09', '2014-06-12 09:10:09', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLITTON, A Fine Camera Bag company that wants you to see the world with childlike curiosity.  We want you to explore the wonders that are in front of you and allow your imagination to run free and be amazed.  We aim to bring a renewing luxury in the world of photography.  Be your own visionary and set yourself free with our captivating designs that promise to achieve modern elegance and smart functionality. Designed by Litton Ludwig.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '100-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 09:10:09', '2014-06-12 09:10:09', '', 100, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/100-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(189, 4, '2014-06-12 09:17:28', '2014-06-12 09:17:28', 'CARE INFORMATION\nOur leathers have been treated and are water and scratch resistant. Should your handbag become wet, wipe gently dry with a soft cloth. for regular cleaning, a damp cloth and mild leather cream may be applied.\n\nIf the bag becomes misshapen through delivery simply remove the dividers and stuff the bag fully and leave for at least 24 hours. Through everyday use it will return to its original shape.', 'Care Info', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '123-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 09:17:28', '2014-06-12 09:17:28', '', 123, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/123-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(190, 4, '2014-06-12 09:17:32', '2014-06-12 09:17:32', 'CARE INFORMATION\r\nOur leathers have been treated and are water and scratch resistant. Should your handbag become wet, wipe gently dry with a soft cloth. for regular cleaning, a damp cloth and mild leather cream may be applied.\r\n\r\nIf the bag becomes misshapen through delivery simply remove the dividers and stuff the bag fully and leave for at least 24 hours. Through everyday use it will return to its original shape.', 'Care Info', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '123-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 09:17:32', '2014-06-12 09:17:32', '', 123, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/123-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
