(209, 4, '2014-06-12 10:59:13', '2014-06-12 10:59:13', '<strong><em>ORDERING AND PAYMENT</em></strong>\n\nORDERING\n\nAfter you click "Submit Order" an e-mail confirmation will be sent confirming that your order is successful.\n\nPAYMENT\n\nWe accept: Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover and PayPal. US dollar amounts are displayed\n\nTAXES\n\nWe are required to collect local sales tax in Hawaii where Litton fine camera bags has a physical presence. A physical presence can be a store, warehouse or contact center.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><em>DISPATCH AND SHIPPING</em></strong>\n\nDISPATCH\n\nWe aim to dispatch all orders within 48 hours, although there may be a slight delay during exceptionally busy periods such as our seasonal sales. Estimated delivery times should be used as a guide only and commence from the day of dispatch. LITTON Fine Camera Bags is not responsible for delays caused by customs clearance.\nOrders received after 11am PST will be processed the next business day. Orders received Saturday and Sunday will be processed on the following Monday, excluding federal holidays.\n\nPACKAGING\n\nOur bags come packaged in a protective LITTON dust bag and arrive in tissue paper and our signature presentation box.\n\nSHIPPING TIME\n\nLITTON fine camera bags are shipped from Honolulu, Hawaii and you should allow 4-7 business days for delivery. Overnight service is only available for the state of Hawaii.\n\nTRACKING\n\nOnce your order has been dispatched you will receive an email with your tracking code, so that you can monitor your delivery until it arrives.\nSIGNATURE REQUIRED UPON DELIVERY\n\nA signature is required upon receipt of your package. If the carrier makes several attempts and does not hear from you, they will return the package to LITTON fine camera bags after a week. Customer is responsible for the second shipping cost.\n\nWe do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address.\n\nINTERNATIONAL SHIPPING\n\nInternational orders are subject to customs inspection, duties and fees. Please be advised that it is your responsibility to pay all the fees applicable to the appropriate authorities when your product arrives to your country. Each country practices their own customs rules and regulations and LITTON fine camera bags is not responsible for any additional fee charged by the authorities of your country. Your item may not be released to you if the duties and fees are not paid by you. Please contact your local customs office for further information.\n\nIf your bag is returned to us we will issue a refund to your account within 10 days of receiving the return item. Shipping and handling charges are non-refundable.\n\nFREE SHIPPING\n\nFree shipping for bags shipped within the U.S. offer valid on bags purchased from littonbags.com only. Product ships from our warehouse within 1-2 business days via FedEx Home Delivery from Honolulu, Hawaii. We do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address. Signature required upon delivery.\n\nEstimated shipping schedule for free shipping:\n\nFrom Hawaii to Hawaii - 1 Business day\nFrom Hawaii to California - 4 Business days\nFrom Hawaii to Illinois - 6 Business days\nFrom Hawaii to Maine - 7 Business days', 'Delivery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '125-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 10:59:13', '2014-06-12 10:59:13', '', 125, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/125-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(211, 4, '2014-06-12 10:45:12', '2014-06-12 10:45:12', 'ORDERING AND PAYMENT\r\nORDERING\r\nAfter you click "Submit Order" an e-mail confirmation will be sent confirming that your order is successful.\r\nPAYMENT\r\nWe accept: Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover and PayPal. US dollar amounts are displayed\r\nTAXES\r\nWe are required to collect local sales tax in Hawaii where Litton fine camera bags has a physical presence. A physical presence can be a store, warehouse or contact center.\r\nDISPATCH AND SHIPPING\r\nDISPATCH\r\nWe aim to dispatch all orders within 48 hours, although there may be a slight delay during exceptionally busy periods such as our seasonal sales. Estimated delivery times should be used as a guide only and commence from the day of dispatch. LITTON Fine Camera Bags is not responsible for delays caused by customs clearance.\r\nOrders received after 11am PST will be processed the next business day. Orders received Saturday and Sunday will be processed on the following Monday, excluding federal holidays.\r\nPACKAGING\r\nOur bags come packaged in a protective LITTON dust bag and arrive in tissue paper and our signature presentation box.\r\nSHIPPING TIME\r\n\r\nLITTON fine camera bags are shipped from Honolulu, Hawaii and you should allow 4-7 business days for delivery. Overnight service is only available for the state of Hawaii.\r\n\r\nTRACKING\r\nOnce your order has been dispatched you will receive an email with your tracking code, so that you can monitor your delivery until it arrives.\r\nSIGNATURE REQUIRED UPON DELIVERY\r\n\r\nA signature is required upon receipt of your package. If the carrier makes several attempts and does not hear from you, they will return the package to LITTON fine camera bags after a week. Customer is responsible for the second shipping cost.\r\n\r\nWe do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address.\r\n\r\nINTERNATIONAL SHIPPING\r\n\r\nInternational orders are subject to customs inspection, duties and fees. Please be advised that it is your responsibility to pay all the fees applicable to the appropriate authorities when your product arrives to your country. Each country practices their own customs rules and regulations and LITTON fine camera bags is not responsible for any additional fee charged by the authorities of your country. Your item may not be released to you if the duties and fees are not paid by you. Please contact your local customs office for further information.\r\n\r\nIf your bag is returned to us we will issue a refund to your account within 10 days of receiving the return item. Shipping and handling charges are non-refundable.\r\n\r\nFREE SHIPPING\r\nFree shipping for bags shipped within the U.S. offer valid on bags purchased from littonbags.com only. Product ships from our warehouse within 1-2 business days via FedEx Home Delivery from Honolulu, Hawaii. We do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address. Signature required upon delivery.\r\n\r\nEstimated shipping schedule for free shipping:\r\n\r\nFrom Hawaii to Hawaii - 1 Business day\r\nFrom Hawaii to California - 4 Business days\r\nFrom Hawaii to Illinois - 6 Business days\r\nFrom Hawaii to Maine - 7 Business days', 'Delivery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 10:45:12', '2014-06-12 10:45:12', '', 125, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/125-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(212, 4, '2014-06-12 10:46:43', '2014-06-12 10:46:43', '', 'Plane', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'plane', '', '', '2014-06-12 10:46:43', '2014-06-12 10:46:43', '', 125, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Plane.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(213, 4, '2014-06-12 10:51:54', '2014-06-12 10:51:54', '<em>ORDERING AND PAYMENT</em>\r\n\r\nORDERING\r\n\r\nAfter you click "Submit Order" an e-mail confirmation will be sent confirming that your order is successful.\r\n\r\nPAYMENT\r\n\r\nWe accept: Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover and PayPal. US dollar amounts are displayed\r\n\r\nTAXES\r\n\r\nWe are required to collect local sales tax in Hawaii where Litton fine camera bags has a physical presence. A physical presence can be a store, warehouse or contact center.\r\n\r\n<em>DISPATCH AND SHIPPING</em>\r\n\r\nDISPATCH\r\n\r\nWe aim to dispatch all orders within 48 hours, although there may be a slight delay during exceptionally busy periods such as our seasonal sales. Estimated delivery times should be used as a guide only and commence from the day of dispatch. LITTON Fine Camera Bags is not responsible for delays caused by customs clearance.\r\nOrders received after 11am PST will be processed the next business day. Orders received Saturday and Sunday will be processed on the following Monday, excluding federal holidays.\r\n\r\nPACKAGING\r\n\r\nOur bags come packaged in a protective LITTON dust bag and arrive in tissue paper and our signature presentation box.\r\n\r\nSHIPPING TIME\r\n\r\nLITTON fine camera bags are shipped from Honolulu, Hawaii and you should allow 4-7 business days for delivery. Overnight service is only available for the state of Hawaii.\r\n\r\nTRACKING\r\n\r\nOnce your order has been dispatched you will receive an email with your tracking code, so that you can monitor your delivery until it arrives.\r\nSIGNATURE REQUIRED UPON DELIVERY\r\n\r\nA signature is required upon receipt of your package. If the carrier makes several attempts and does not hear from you, they will return the package to LITTON fine camera bags after a week. Customer is responsible for the second shipping cost.\r\n\r\nWe do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address.\r\n\r\nINTERNATIONAL SHIPPING\r\n\r\nInternational orders are subject to customs inspection, duties and fees. Please be advised that it is your responsibility to pay all the fees applicable to the appropriate authorities when your product arrives to your country. Each country practices their own customs rules and regulations and LITTON fine camera bags is not responsible for any additional fee charged by the authorities of your country. Your item may not be released to you if the duties and fees are not paid by you. Please contact your local customs office for further information.\r\n\r\nIf your bag is returned to us we will issue a refund to your account within 10 days of receiving the return item. Shipping and handling charges are non-refundable.\r\n\r\nFREE SHIPPING\r\n\r\nFree shipping for bags shipped within the U.S. offer valid on bags purchased from littonbags.com only. Product ships from our warehouse within 1-2 business days via FedEx Home Delivery from Honolulu, Hawaii. We do not ship to PO boxes, please provide a physical address. Signature required upon delivery.\r\n\r\nEstimated shipping schedule for free shipping:\r\n\r\nFrom Hawaii to Hawaii - 1 Business day\r\nFrom Hawaii to California - 4 Business days\r\nFrom Hawaii to Illinois - 6 Business days\r\nFrom Hawaii to Maine - 7 Business days', 'Delivery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-12 10:51:54', '2014-06-12 10:51:54', '', 125, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/125-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
