(121, 3, '2013-12-24 07:24:40', '2013-12-24 07:24:40', 'Return and Exchange\r\nWe apologize for any inconvenience and will do our best to assist you.\r\n\r\nReturns and exchanges are excepted within 10 days of receiving your product.  Refunds will be made to the credit or debit card used to purchase.  The product must be in perfect unused condition and include all accessories included.   Please contact us select the Return/Exchanges as the subject and notify us of your return or request for an exchange.\r\n\r\nWe strongly recommend when returning items to us you use recorded or special delivery as we are unable to refund or exchange items that are lost in the post.  All goods shall remain your responsibility until we receive them.\r\n\r\nPlease fill out the return/exchange form included in your shipment and a copy of your sales receipt or packing slip, and send to the address provided below.\r\n\r\nMost returns are processed and credited within  within ten days of receipt. We will send you an email confirming that your return or exchange has been processed.  Return shipping and handling paid to return or exchange the product is non-refundable.\r\n\r\nLitton Fine Camera Bags\r\nP.O. BOX 10734\r\nHonolulu, HI 96816\r\n\r\nCancellation\r\nIf you cancel before the delivery of any goods your money will be refunded and the goods will not be delivered.', 'Returns', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'returns', '', '', '2014-06-12 11:56:48', '2014-06-12 11:56:48', '', 0, 'http://dev.littonbags.com/?page_id=121', 0, 'page', '', 0),
